title: Utah police release body camera video related to Gabby Petito case
author: ABC Action News
description: Police in Utah released body camera video related to an August 12 call involving Gabby Petito and Brian Laundrie. Police responded after a witness called to report the couple fighting. An officer later wrote in a report that the incident between the couple did not "escalate to a level of domestic violence, as much as that of a mental health crisis."
